          @vidro3 N vs C was 3-1. Add this to the tonight's score, and you'll get the winner. If the sum is a draw, (2-0 for chelsea making it 3-3 on aggregate) then they see who scored more goals away from home (In this case, Chelsea wins because of that first goal in their total) If the game ends 3-1 for Chelsea, making the aggregate 4-4 with equal goals away from home, a PK shootout occurs.
